itunes:subtitle: The streetwear publications plans to launch its own private label within the year, and projects that its online shop will encompass up to 50 percent of overall business within five years. Founder David Fischer talks about the new project on the latest Bo.
description:
The streetwear publications plans to launch its own private label within the year, and projects that its online shop will encompass up to 50 percent of overall business within five years. Founder David Fischer talks about the new project on the latest BoF Podcast.
